Jury :=20

DR. Nathalie Aussenac-Gilles, Universit=C3=A9 de Toulouse, IRIT, CNRS, Toul=
ouse , reviewer=20

Pr. Igor Boguslavsky, Universidad Polit=C3=A9cnica de Madrid & Russian Acad=
emy of Sciences, Moscow , reviewer=20

